### 1. Login do super admin
# @name adminLogin
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "super@email.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 2. Guardar token (CORRIGIDO)
@tokenAdmin = {{adminLogin.response.body.access_token}}

### 3. Criar organização (com token)
POST http://localhost:3000/admin/create-organization
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenAdmin}} 
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "organizationNome": "org223",
  "adminNome": "a1",
  "adminEmail": "a1233@email.com",
  "adminSenha": "123456"
}

### 4. Criar usuário comum (CORRIGIDO)
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenAdmin}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "joao",
  "email": "rafael122@email.com",
  "senha": "123456",
  "organizationId": "09a0d868-762f-41c4-82d4-efddd990179e",
  "role": "LIDER"
}

### 5. Listar usuários (CORRIGIDO)
GET http://localhost:3000/users
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenAdmin}}

### 6. Criar super admin via endpoint admin
POST http://localhost:3000/users/admin
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenAdmin}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Super Admin 2",
  "email": "super1@email.com",
  "senha": "123456"
}


